    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with cosmetic wear consistent with age, but it still starts up, tracks straight, and has a strong-running engine with good oil pressure and a responsive automatic transmission. Suspension feels composed for what it is, braking is predictable, and it\u2019s a solid candidate for a dependable budget commuter, weekend runabout, or project build. Not a show car, but the core mechanical package is there and it offers a lot of usable vehicle for the money. Priced to move for someone who values function over flawless cosmetics.",
